<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body class="bg-image bg-cover" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/reserve/EnF7DhHROS8OMEp2pCkx_Dufer%20food%20overhead%20hig%20res.jpg?q=80&w=1756&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover; height: 100vh">
    <div class="my-5 mx-5 text-success">
        <h1>Update <%= meal.dayOfTheWeek %> meals</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="mx-5">
        <form action="/show/<%= meal._id %>?_method=PUT" method="post">
            <div class="row">
                <input type="text" name="mealOne" placeholder="Breakfast description" value="<%= meal.mealOne %>" class="col-8">
                <input type="number" name="howManyPeopleBreakfast" placeholder="How many?" value="<%= meal.howManyPeopleBreakfast %>" class="col-1">
                <input type="checkbox" name="isItPreparedOne" <%= meal.isItPreparedOne ? "checked" : "" %> class="col-3">
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <input type="text" name="mealTwo" placeholder="Lunch description" value="<%= meal.mealTwo %>" class="col-8">
                <input type="number" name="howManyPeopleLunch" placeholder="How many?" value="<%= meal.howManyPeopleLunch %>" class="col-1">
                <input type="checkbox" name="isItPreparedTwo" <%= meal.isItPreparedTwo ? "checked" : "" %> class="col-3">
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <input type="text" name="mealThree" placeholder="Dinner description" value="<%= meal.mealThree %>" class="col-8">
                <input type="number" name="howManyPeopleDinner" placeholder="How many?" value="<%= meal.howManyPeopleDinner %>" class="col-1">
                <input type="checkbox" name="isItPreparedThree" <%= meal.isItPreparedThree ? "checked" : "" %> class="col-3">
            </div>

            <input type="submit" value="Update <%= meal.dayOfTheWeek %>" class="my-3 btn btn-primary">
        </form>
    </div>

<!-- offcanvas -->
    <div class="my-4 mx-5">
        <button class="btn btn-success" type="button" data-bs-toggle="offcanvas" data-bs-target="#offcanvasExample" aria-controls="offcanvasExample">
        More food options
        </button>
    </div>
    <div class="offcanvas offcanvas-end bg-secondary text-light" tabindex="-1" id="offcanvasExample" aria-labelledby="offcanvasExampleLabel">
        <div class="offcanvas-header">
            <h5 class="offcanvas-title" id="offcanvasExampleLabel">
                MORE FOOD!!!
            </h5>
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="offcanvas" aria-label="Close"></button>
        </div>
    <div class="offcanvas-body">
      <div>
        Each dropdown gives you more options if you run into a road block on what to eat.  
      </div>

      <div class="dropdown mt-3">
        <div class="container px-4 text-start my-5">
            <button class="btn btn-primary dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
            Breakfast Options
            </button>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Cereal</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Eggs and Toast on wheat bread</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Oatmeal with 1 scoop of chunky peanut butter</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Ka'Chava shake with banana and avacado</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Go out an buy something on your way to work, lazy</a></li>
                </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="container px-4 text-center my-5">
            <button class="btn btn-warning dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                Lunch Options
            </button>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Chicken wrap with apple</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Pizza</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">PB & J</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Soup</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Buy something on your break, McSpendy Pants</a></li>
                </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="container px-4 text-end my-5">
            <button class="btn btn-success dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                Dinner Options
            </button>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Din1</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Din2</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Din3</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Din4</a></li>
                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Din5</a></li>
                </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    </div>
    <div class="my-5 mx-5">
        <a href="/">
            <button class="btn btn-info">
                <h5>Back to the week</h5>
            </button>
        </a>
    </div>
